Title: Smart-PING should (optionally) use ICMP payload
Component: core
Class: nastiness
State: done
Date: 2014-04-14 16:05:46
Targetversion: next

Currently the Smart-PING packets do not contain any payload. Some firewalls
seem to drop these packages and rather exception "conventional" 64 Byte
payload - like the normal ping without any options. We should (optionally)
implement that behaviour.

2014-12-01 16:37:42: changed state open -> done
